聞？<br />\n<br />\n我話你知，香港核心價值只有一個，就係買樓，樓就係一切，係萬物之本。<br />\n<br />\n咩學業壓力呀，興趣呀，個人修養呀，文化呀，道德呀，全部毫無價值！你只要有樓，理得你殺人放火，就係贏家。<br />\n<br />\n郁d就自殺，連學生階段呢個easy mode都過唔到，仲點做大人？<br />\n<br />\n有樓既話，所有問題都唔會係問題。"},{"pid":"1dde54b3bfed799f116b85e8a26deb8181758b41","tid":1101336,"uid":838,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T03:42:57.000Z","msg":"教 局 副 局 長 蔡 若 蓮 兒 子 墮 樓 亡 (8)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/993565\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/993565</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"68a98f8efe4f6b697df37c1045e276dd236ba50d","tid":1101336,"uid":151933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T03:44:16.000Z","msg":"取消tsa啦屌"},{"pid":"0bcf3c39a25de7dac87928f9b43534e7915edec7","tid":1101336,"uid":143018,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T03:53:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>教育局稱留意到最近兩個學年相關個案較以往多，除繼續推行學校訓育及輔導， 亦會加強推動反欺凌及尊重別人的活動</blockquote><br />\n點都好，總之就係學校 學生 家長嘅問題，教育局就完全冇問題<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/NG6-01_MVSgx_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FNG6-01_MVSgx_1200x0.png&h=f50a13b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20160312/s00001/1457742868669_8B81E4CD54EE02E233EAD7EDF933E32A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20160312%2Fs00001%2F1457742868669_8B81E4CD54EE02E233EAD7EDF933E32A.jpg&h=086781f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20160308/s00001/1457440447336SL4_AF1CA6F0810268091BCD55073F48410B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20160308%2Fs00001%2F1457440447336SL4_AF1CA6F0810268091BCD55073F48410B.jpg&h=646aceb4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c057d7ea2bf70e9f5be0a656e0a7f8456306aca","tid":1101336,"uid":33441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T03:55:36.000Z","msg":"精